-- ==========================================================================
-- 083: Central Curated Knowledge v2 — substantial expansion
--
-- Sprint A (078) seeded ~98 entities + ~106 relationships across six
-- domains. The reasoning engine has since outgrown the knowledge base
-- (Sprint G observation). This migration triples the graph with
-- substantive, cited facts:
--
--   * ~30 new provenance records (IRS Pubs, 26 USC sections,
--     CFP Board, FINRA, CFPB, DOL ERISA, ACSM/AHA/USDA, NIH/PubMed,
--     ABA RPTE, UTC/UPC, va.gov, 38 USC/38 CFR, …).
--   * ~225 new ontology_entities covering CFP concepts, retirement
--     vehicles, debt/credit, mortgage products, tax concepts,
--     insurance lines, HSA/FSA mechanics, employer benefits,
--     occupations, certifications, promotion patterns, salary curves,
--     degrees + alt credentials, GI Bill / VR&E / TAP, scholarships,
--     macronutrients, training periodization, sleep science,
--     behavior change frameworks, wills/trusts/POA, beneficiary
--     designations, guardianship, business succession, VA
--     compensation tables.
--   * ~280 new ontology_relationships expressing the cross-domain
--     edges the AdvisorReasoningService traverses.
--
-- Every row: source, confidence_score, version, provenance JSONB +
-- provenance_id pointing to central.provenance_records. review_status
-- = 'approved' for all rows in this batch. ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING
-- throughout so re-runs are safe.
-- ==========================================================================


